author: Matt Pentz
title: Video: Sounders goalkeeper Stefan Frei discusses the ‘long, grueling’ MLS season
text:
Sounders goalkeeper Stefan Frei spoke to local media following Tuesday’s practice session at Starfire Sports Complex, discussing the “long, grueling” Major League Soccer and the effect of the recent late-season bye weekend.
Matt Pentz : 206-464-3184 or mpentz@seattletimes.com ; on Twitter: @mattpentz . Matt Pentz covers Sounders FC, Reign FC, MLS and world soccer for The Seattle Times throughout the year.
